title: NSCLC EMC TB0069tu
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 6 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 20 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Human Genome U133 plus 2.0 array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station Fluidics 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneArray scanner 3000
description: Gene expression data from primary NSCLC
data_processing: The data was normalized by Robust Multi-Array average (RMA) algorithm. Intensities of probe sets lower than 30 were reset to 30.The intensity values of individual probe sets in each sample were then displayed as the log 2 of the deviations to the calculated geometric means for that probe sets.

hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 20 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Human Genome U133 plus 2.0 array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station Fluidics 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneArray scanner 3000
description: Gene expression data from normal lung
data_processing: The data was normalized by Robust Multi-Array average (RMA) algorithm. Intensities of probe sets lower than 30 were reset to 30.The intensity values of individual probe sets in each sample were then displayed as the log 2 of the deviations to the calculated geometric means for that probe sets.

hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 20 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Human Genome U133 plus 2.0 array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station Fluidics 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneArray scanner 3000
description: Gene expression data from primary NSCLC
data_processing: The data was normalized by Robust Multi-Array average (RMA) algorithm. Intensities of probe sets lower than 30 were reset to 30.The intensity values of individual probe sets in each sample were then displayed as the log 2 of the deviations to the calculated geometric means for that probe sets.

hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 20 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Human Genome U133 plus 2.0 array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station Fluidics 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneArray scanner 3000
description: Gene expression data from primary NSCLC
data_processing: The data was normalized by Robust Multi-Array average (RMA) algorithm. Intensities of probe sets lower than 30 were reset to 30.The intensity values of individual probe sets in each sample were then displayed as the log 2 of the deviations to the calculated geometric means for that probe sets.
